verbose_text: RAGE expression (+/-SE) was upregulated in the heart, aorta and subcutaneous adipose tissue (SAT) by 1.83 +/- 0.90, 1.45 +/- 1.31 and 2.12 +/- 1.35 fold respectively, and was downregulated in the liver, kidney, quadriceps femoris (QF) and visceral adipose tissue (VAT) by 2.22 +/- 0.29, 1.65 +/- 0.92, 2.03 +/- 0.26 and 2.75 +/- 0.27 fold respectively.
